node.text:
venus in libra likes symmetry. and order. and no conflict.

from august 16th to september 10th, venus will be in its home sign of libra. 

with libra being the masculine/assertive home of venusian pleasure, it often takes the form of actively encouraging social harmony. this is in contrast to taurus who often just wants sensory harmony in a passive way. 

so as venus in libra values the air sign emphasis on logic and reason to work things out, we can expect an easier time reaching understandings in our conversations and relationships. 

and if there’s anything venus in libra values, it’s the depth of surface placidity: sometimes just looking good or having a pleasing appearance makes things feel better deep down. 

like the fact that i was able to get this photo, standing on the dancer’s platform in the middle of a restaurant, which is most definitely not allowed, without anyone causing any issues. aesthetic respect. 

x
